{
  "stem": "22582.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they assigned us to certain work in-- to go to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the barracks were the worst, because whoever didn't have money, and they were [? last ?] one.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Slowly, whoever had some money could help himself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't have money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't have money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't have nothing to trade, so I was assigned to worst work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then whenever they had some kind of-- somehow, they were always sending people away, to new camps or bad camps or better places.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But you never knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, when you-- when you were at a place, you knew the place where you were, and you knew what you had to expect.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If you came to Plaszow, it was very bad, but you knew what it was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, you didn't know where they were sending you, and if-- if this was a people-- a-- a place to-- to kill or to live.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So whenever they wanted to send us out, somehow they went-- the people couldn't help themself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was on the list, because I had the worst place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I couldn't buy myself out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, I had, as I mentioned before, I put away some jewelry and money, whatever I had, and put in with somebody who I didn't know, but through my friend.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was supposed to be a very honest man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- but it took time till you get.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You come to Plaszow, and it was-- everything was very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, you came to a new place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You had to know what to meet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You had to get some contact.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- and some people who were more closely with this process, they were first to get their things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were first.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
